{"ID":"20260704130658-exvodjj","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260704130658-exvodjj","title":"Concept","type":"doc","updated":"20260705000658"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260705000658-fvd97bn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260705000658-fvd97bn","updated":"20260704152948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"SSE is a method to get reponses in real time alternativly from websockets, its a better way to do pooling without having to open and close the connection every time, sending a bunch of headers and overloading the traffic and the server. "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"The main difference between websockets and SSE is the simplicity of implementation, unidirectional and less dedicated infrastructure."}]},{"ID":"20260704152554-hdwtiz9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260704152554-hdwtiz9","updated":"20260704152636"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Types of approunch:"}]},{"ID":"20260704152514-mm264q5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260704152514-mm264q5","updated":"20260704152755"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"style":"width: 355px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20260705022542-1v9j3fa.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 355px;\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20260705022623-2wfrhwk.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"style":"width: 565px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Ty